The weather is too hot.

31
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:19,960
- I have no appetite.
- All right.

32
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,079
Wait there.

33
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,750
I'll be there in a second.

34
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:37,790
In the past 3 years,

35
