He is breaking records as the top sprinter of all time.

37
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:53,749
Jia Lin, do you know the guy over there?

38
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,839
I don't.

39
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,690
He's very handsome.

40
00:03:56,690 --> 00:03:59,030
- Don't you think?
- That's right.

41
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,949
You'll be competing this afternoon.

42
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,119
Why are you eating so much?

43
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:38,250
The amount I eat won't affect my performance.

44
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:41,440
South Lake University's coach is scouting talents today.

45
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,870
I know.

46
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,509
Good luck.

47
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:47,509
Horse Face's first choice isn't South Lake University.

48
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:49,510
You have a chance.

49
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,670
I don't care about his goals.

50
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:06,680
I will surely win this time.

51
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,119
Duan Yu Cheng,

52
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:15,070
how many events have you signed up for?

53
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,239
Right now, there are three events

54
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,640
